    <h1>Customer Lifetime Value (CLV)</h1>
    <p class="description">The total revenue a single customer generates across the entire relationship. CLV is the number that decides <strong>how much you can spend to acquire</strong> a customer — and the growth lever most under-optimised inside B2B and DTC.</p>
